      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You extract academic assignment details from a university/course email. Return structured JSON.\n\nRules:\n- Set \"hasDeadline\" to true ONLY if the email mentions a concrete due date / submission deadline for a task, assignment, quiz, project or exam. Otherwise set it false and leave the other fields as empty strings.\n- \"deadline\": normalise to an ISO date (YYYY-MM-DD) when a specific date is present; include time if given. If only relative wording exists (e.g. \"next Friday\") keep the original wording.\n- \"courseName\": the course/subject name or code. \"assignmentName\": the task/assignment title.\n- \"marks\": the marks/weight/points if stated (e.g. \"20\", \"10%\"), else \"\".\n- \"submissionLink\": a submission or LMS URL if present, else \"\".\n- Never invent values. Use \"\" for anything not stated.\n\n--- EMAIL ---\nSubject: {{ $json.subject }}\nFrom: {{ $json.from }}\n\nBody:\n{{ $json.body }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "batching": {}
      },
